The paper deals with the problem of teaching an artificial intelligence agent to shepherd a swarm, which involves decision-making in complex and dynamic environments. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with control and decision-making, which are also relevant to the sub-categories of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA).
